import React from "react";
import IconCircleONotch from "react-icons/fa/circle-o-notch";
 
import mergeProps from "../utils/merge-props";
import rotate from "../styles/animations/rotate.animate";
 
export default function IconLoading(props) {
  const iconProps = {
    "data-cm-type": "loadingIcon",
    className: rotate()
  };
 
  const newProps = mergeProps(iconProps,props);
 
  return (
    <IconCircleONotch {...newProps} />
  );
}
